572
00:30:13,811 --> 00:30:15,521
guincho, sistema de acionamento,

573
00:30:15,605 --> 00:30:17,565
controles auxiliares, bombas d'água,

574
00:30:17,648 --> 00:30:18,774
detectores de fumaça.

575
00:30:19,483 --> 00:30:20,568
O senhor está suando tanto

576
00:30:20,651 --> 00:30:23,154
