636
00:33:14,325 --> 00:33:17,495
Nós desligamos. O trem todo desliga.

637
00:33:18,788 --> 00:33:20,373
Entende, Sr. Williams?

638
00:33:21,249 --> 00:33:22,792
Quer remédio, Sr. Vidrine?

639
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:27,755
Estou tentando avaliar o quanto

640
00:33:27,838 --> 00:33:30,258
